ACTION :[2192] 'DECLARE
  link_failed boolean;

BEGIN
       FOR f IN (  SELECT *
                     FROM test_db
                   where field1 not in ('teststring')
                     and field1 = upper('teststring2')
                     and test_db = upper('test.domain')
                 ORDER BY field, test_db)
       LOOP
           TEST.create_job (
               job_name     => f.owner || '.TESTSTRING',
               job_type     => 'TESTSTRING',
               job_action   =>    'TESTSTRING '
                               || '  TESTSTRING; '
                               || 'TESTSTRING '
                               || '  SELECT dummy into x from TEST@'
                               || f.test3
                               || '  ;'
                               || '  TEST.put_line('''
                               || f.test2
                               || ' '
                               || f.test
                               || '     VALID !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!'');'
                               || 'END ; ');

          BEGIN
               TEST.run_job (f.owner || '.TESTSTRING ', TRUE);
           EXCEPTION
               WHEN OTHERS
               THEN
                   link_failed:=true;
                   TEST.put_line (
                          f.owner
                       || ' '
                       || f.db_link
                       || ' INVALID (ORA'
                       || SQLCODE
                       || ')');
           END;

           TEST.job (f.owner || ' . TESTSTRING ');

           if link_failed THEN
              TEST.put_line (
                     f.owner
                  || ' '
                  || f.TEST
                  || ' TESTSTRING - TEST (ORA'
                  || SQLCODE
                  || ')');
              insert into TEST.somestring
                values (f.owner, f.test, 'INVALID', sysdate);
              commit;
           else
              insert into TEST.somestring
                values (f.owner, f.test, 'VALID', sysdate);
              commit;
           end if;

       END LOOP;
END;'
